---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import WaitlistDirectoryWrapper from '../../components/interactive/WaitlistDirectoryWrapper.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Waitlist Times | Twilight Psychology"
  description="Current waitlist times at Twilight Psychology in Lexington, KY for evaluations, therapy, and medication management."
>
  <section class="bg-site-bg min-h-screen py-24 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <header class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-site-text mb-4">
          Waitlist <span class="text-cta">Times</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-sand text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Filter by service or state to view current wait times for our providers.
        </p>
      </header>

      <WaitlistDirectoryWrapper />
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-12 text-sm text-sand">
      <p>
        * Insurance-based psychological testing depends on medical-necessity review, prior authorization, and the
        number of testing hours a plan approves. 
      </p>
      <p>KY, OH, NM, and TN are Twilight Psychology's licensed states. Remote services extend to 40+ additional states through the PSYPACT compact. For a full list, visit <a href="https://psypact.gov/page/psypactmap" class="text-cta underline">Psypact Map</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>